    GH["рџ”· GitHub, Inc.\n(Microsoft subsidiary)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nRole: Data Processor\nGoverning doc: GitHub DPA +\nGitHub Generative AI Services Terms\n(eff. March 5, 2026)\nProcessing: United States"]

    MSFT["рџ”· Microsoft Corporation\n(Azure)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nRole: Sub-processor\nService: AI Inference (fine-tuned models)\nGoverning doc: Microsoft Product Terms\nfor GitHub Offerings\nProcessing: United States"]

    OAI["рџџҰ OpenAI, L.L.C.\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nRole: Sub-processor\nService: AI Inference (GPT/Codex)\nGoverning doc: GitHubвЂ“OpenAI\nZDR Agreement\nвљ  Customer has no direct DPA\nProcessing: United States\nInfra: Azure + OpenAI own DC"]

    ANTH["рџ”ө Anthropic PBC\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nRole: Sub-processor\nService: AI Inference (Claude)\nGoverning doc: GitHubвЂ“Anthropic\nZDR Agreement\nвљ  ZDR covers GA features ONLY\nвљ  Preview features: may retain data\nвљ  Customer has no direct DPA\nProcessing: United States"]

    AWS["рџџ  Amazon Web Services, Inc.\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nRole: Sub-processor\nService: AI Inference (Bedrock вЂ“\nhosts Claude models)\nGoverning doc: GitHubвЂ“AWS agreement\nCommitment: No storage, no logging,\nno training\nвљ  Customer has no direct DPA\nProcessing: United States"]

    GCP["рџџұ Google Cloud Platform\n(Google LLC)\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nRole: Sub-processor\nService: AI Inference (Gemini +\nsome Claude via Vertex AI)\nGoverning doc: GitHubвЂ“Google agreement\nCommitment: No training, no abuse logging\nвљ  NO explicit ZDR term documented\nвљ  Customer has no direct DPA\nProcessing: United States,\nBelgium, Singapore"]

    FW["в¬› Fireworks AI, Inc.\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nRole: Sub-processor\nService: AI Inference\nGoverning doc: GitHubвЂ“Fireworks agreement\nвљ  Limited public documentation\nвљ  Customer has no direct DPA\nProcessing: United States"]

